2. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) - The paper mentions the application of emotion recognition in human-computer interaction, indicating a possible fit for this sub-category.
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with processing and analyzing images, which is a common task in multimedia applications.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a machine learning approach for emotion recognition, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses Principal Component Analysis (PCA) for dimensionality reduction and modeling the variation pattern, which are common techniques in machine learning.
